---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — LUTkyLab"
  description="LUTkyLab participates in the Amazon Associates Program and other affiliate programs. Learn how this works and how it affects our recommendations."
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[720px] px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
    <p class="text-[#9CA3AF] mb-2 text-sm">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="prose">
      <h2>Amazon Associates</h2>
      <p>
        LUTkyLab (lutkylab.com) is a participant in the Amazon Services LLC Associates Program, an affiliate advertising program designed to provide a means for sites to earn advertising fees by advertising and linking to Amazon.com. As an Amazon Associate, I earn from qualifying purchases.
      </p>

      <h2>What this means for you</h2>
      <p>
        When you click an Amazon link on this site and make a purchase, I receive a small commission — typically 1–4% of the sale price. This costs you nothing extra. The price you pay is exactly the same whether you use my link or go directly to Amazon.
      </p>

      <h2>My editorial standards</h2>
      <p>
        I only recommend products I have actually used or would genuinely consider buying. Affiliate relationships do not influence my reviews or rankings. If a product has a real weakness, I will say so even if it earns me commission.
      </p>
      <p>
        Products I recommend are chosen based on my personal testing and experience — not because they have the highest affiliate payout.
      </p>

      <h2>Sponsored content</h2>
      <p>
        If I ever publish sponsored content (paid reviews, brand partnerships), it will be clearly labeled as "Sponsored" at the top of the post. To date, all content on this site is independently produced.
      </p>

      <h2>Other affiliate programs</h2>
      <p>
        I may occasionally link to other retailers or affiliate programs beyond Amazon. Any such links are marked with rel="sponsored nofollow" and will be disclosed in context.
      </p>

      <h2>Questions</h2>
      <p>
        If you have questions about this disclosure or how affiliate links work on this site, <a href="/contact">contact me</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
